name: PixelFem #21 - Laverie Valee
description:
Laverie Valee, also known ‘Charmion.’ was a Trapeze Artist and a Strongwoman, 1897 Charmion built her act around a memorable routine which opened with her on-stage entrance dressed in full Victorian street attire. She subsequently mounted the trapeze and disrobed down to her acrobat leotards in the midst of the trapeze's swinging motion.

✺This work is part of PixelFems, an evolving project on the Tezos blockchain celebrating iconic women from the past and present✺
